### Test Sakila CRUD API
### Make sure the application is running on http://localhost:8080

### ===== ACTOR ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all actors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/actors

### Get actor by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/actors/1

### Create new actor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/actors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Leonardo",
  "lastName": "DiCaprio"
}

### Update actor
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/actors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "PENELOPE",
  "lastName": "GUINESS-UPDATED"
}

### Search actors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/actors/search?keyword=PENELOPE

### Delete actor (use a valid ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/actors/201


