### ===== FILM ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all films
GET http://localhost:8080/api/films

### Get film by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/films/1

### Create new film
POST http://localhost:8080/api/films
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix Resurrections",
  "description": "Return to a world of two realities",
  "releaseYear": 2021,
  "languageId": 1,
  "rentalDuration": 5,
  "rentalRate": 4.99,
  "length": 148,
  "replacementCost": 24.99,
  "rating": "R",
  "specialFeatures": "Trailers,Behind the Scenes"
}

### Update film
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/films/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "ACADEMY DINOSAUR - UPDATED",
  "description": "An epic tale updated",
  "releaseYear": 2006,
  "languageId": 1,
  "rentalDuration": 6,
  "rentalRate": 3.99,
