### ===== CUSTOMER ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers

### Get customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1

### Create new customer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": 1,
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "addressId": 5,
  "active": true
}

### Update customer
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeId": 1,
  "firstName": "MARY",
  "lastName": "SMITH-UPDATED",
  "email": "mary.smith.updated@sakilacustomer.org",
  "addressId": 5,
  "active": true
}

### Search customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/search?keyword=MARY

### Get active customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/active

### Delete customer (use a valid ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/customers/600

